comment: /**  * Set the Tomcat base directory. If not specified a temporary directory will be used.  * @param baseDirectory the tomcat base directory  */
code: /**  * Set the Tomcat base directory. If not specified a temporary directory will be used.  * @param baseDirectory the tomcat base directory  */ void setBaseDirectory(File baseDirectory).

comment: /**  * Sets the background processor delay in seconds.  * @param delay the delay in seconds  */
code: /**  * Sets the background processor delay in seconds.  * @param delay the delay in seconds  */ void setBackgroundProcessorDelay(int delay).

comment: /**  * Add {@link TomcatContextCustomizer}s that should be added to the Tomcat  * {@link Context}.  * @param tomcatContextCustomizers the customizers to add  */

comment: /**  * Set the character encoding to use for URL decoding. If not specified 'UTF-8' will  * be used.  * @param uriEncoding the uri encoding to set  */
